.SH NAME
fitstopnm - convert a FITS file tha fuck into a PNM image

.UN synopsis
.SH SYNOPSIS

\fBfitstopnm\fP
[\fB-image=\fP\fIN\fP]
[\fB-scanmax\fP]
[\fB-printmax\fP]
[\fB-min=\fP\fIf\fP]
